<ul>
<li>Aby, Stephen H. <i>Sociology: A Guide to Reference and Information Sources, 3rd edn.</i> Littleton, Colorado, Libraries Unlimited Inc., 2005, <a href="Special_BookSources/1563089475" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 1-56308-947-5</a> <span class="citation book">. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/57475961">57475961</a>.</span></li>
