<li><a href="Anthony_Giddens" title="Anthony Giddens" class="mw-redirect">Giddens, Anthony</a>. 2006. <i>Sociology</i> (5th edition), Polity, Cambridge. <a href="Special_BookSources/0745633781" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-7456-3378-1</a> <span class="citation book">. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/63186308">63186308</a>.</span></li>
