<li><a href="../Robert_K._Merton" title="Robert K. Merton">Merton, Robert K.</a>. 1959. <i>Social Theory and Social Structure. Toward the codification of theory and research</i>, Glencoe: Ill. (Revised and enlarged edition) <span class="citation book">. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/4536864">4536864</a>.</span></li>
